title: Didnt get the Teemoing Icons?
body: So being an icon collector and all, I jumped right at the chance to get more free icons. I played and beat the Teemoing. He was summoned, and we did win. But I never got any icons. Aren't you supposed to get one for his initial summon? and another for winning? Maybe I misunderstood something?

replies.body: I haven't got it either yet. Maybe we must wait longer, but at the same time I see a lot of other people having the icon already

I thought so too. I had to wait a while for the second Worlds Pick Ems Icon thing. But I didn't have to wait this long. I just want to make sure I didn't miss anything and that I will eventually get it.

We're still sending out the icons in waves until **Nov. 17th**, so if you don't have it by the time the 18th rolls around, hit us up in a [support ticket.](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/requests/new)

Let me know if you have any questions.
Got it now, thought it would go quicker
